 <item> <title>U.S. Department of Education Plain Writing Initiative</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/archived-plain-language</link>
 <description>The Plain Writing Act of 2010 requires federal agencies to write &quot;clear Government communication that the public can understand and use.&quot; President Obama also emphasized the importance of establishing &quot;a system of transparency, public participation, and collaboration&quot; in his Jan. 21, 2009, Memorandum on Transparency and Open Government.

</description>
